original_font_information.description: Inspired by the hand painted signs in supermarkets, and the roman structures of the classical alphabets. Poetsen is a display font, but it's not just intenden to be used on big straight to the eye titles, since it has a large x heigth it can be used on short paragraphs in relatively small bodies of text.
